  <brief_title>Trial of Docetaxel Versus Vinorelbine as 1st Line Treatment in Elderly Patients With Non-Small-Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter Randomized Phase II Study of Docetaxel Versus Vinorelbine as First-Line Treatment in Elderly Patients With Advanced Non-Small-Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC)</official_title>
